sources.description:
Trapped In a Cave of Terror!
A loony farmer finds a prehistoric monster hiding in a cavern on his land. To feed his newest critter, the farmer kidnaps three people, who desperately try to escape.

Original title: It's Alive! (1969) 

This movie is subtitled in many languages.

Director: Larry Buchanan
Writers: Larry Buchanan, Richard Matheson
Stars: Tommy Kirk, Shirley Bonne, Bill Thurman, Annabelle Weenick
Genres: Cult classic, Horror, Sci-Fi, Monster movie
